{"title":"linux设置开机启动 systemctl enable","date":"2018-04-09T03:13:00.000Z","link":"post/25","tags":["enable","php","php-fpm","systemctl","开机"],"categories":["Liunx"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:23:52.937Z","content":"<h1 id=\"是超级用户权限下\">是超级用户权限下<a href=\"post/25#是超级用户权限下\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable //这句话的意思就是将那个服务设置开机启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable httpd //设置开机启动httpd服务</span><br><span class=\"line\"># systemctl enable php-fpm //设置php开机启动</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"不是超级用户权限下\">不是超级用户权限下<a href=\"post/25#不是超级用户权限下\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">需要在命令前添加  sudo 指令</span><br><span class=\"line\">例：</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo systemctl enable</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h1 id=\"添加成功会显示\">添加成功会显示<a href=\"post/25#添加成功会显示\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">created symlink from ...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/3941865595.png\" alt=\"symlink.png\" class=\"article-img\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"ssm框架中dao层如何调用数据库中数据spring配置——个人小总结","link":"post/30"},"next":{"title":"在linux中查看mysql数据库中表","link":"post/16"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/25/","toc":[{"title":"是超级用户权限下","id":"是超级用户权限下","index":"1"},{"title":"不是超级用户权限下","id":"不是超级用户权限下","index":"2"},{"title":"添加成功会显示","id":"添加成功会显示","index":"3"}]}